      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be writing this, but it\u2019s time for my absolute pride and joy to find a new garage. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it\u2019s been garage-kept, hand-washed every weekend, and honestly, it still smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and responsive, just the way a well-loved machine should. Aside from maybe a tiny, invisible speck of dust from the drive over, she is truly as perfect as they come. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate her as much as I have. Come on by, let\u2019s chat cars, and you can see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
      "price": 48500.0,
