      "description": "Offered here is a pristine example of the S65-powered E92, a surgical instrument for the tarmac. This chassis has been fastidiously curated, featuring preventative rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells and ARP bolts to ensure bottom-end longevity. The DCT logic has been optimized for lightning-fast actuation, while the EDC suspension remains taut, providing unparalleled lateral stability. Not a hint of VANOS rattle or throttle actuator lag. This isn't just a driver; it's a benchmark-spec machine for the discerning purist who demands mechanical perfection and zero-compromise performance.",
      "price": 49500.0,
